Shikamaru throws a myriad of [[kunai]], all but one of which have [[wire strings]] attached to them, with a single one having explosive grenades instead, at the opponent. He then pulls on the strings, creating a [[wikipedia:Friction|friction]] that cuts down a bunch of tree branches, creating a debris that triggers the grenades, causing an explosion.
